2. In Chrome/Edge, you may need to confirm: "Keep unsafe file"

3. After download completes, locate the file in your Downloads folder

4. RIGHT-CLICK the file and select "Scan with Windows Defender" (or your antivirus)

5. ONLY after confirming your antivirus scan shows clean results, proceed with installation

---

## Installation Steps

1. Download the .rar file using the link above
2. Temporarily disable Windows Defender and any other antivirus software (after verification)
3. Extract the .rar file using the provided password
4. Right-click the `KMSAuto.exe` file and select "Run as administrator"
5. If Windows Defender SmartScreen appears, click "More info" then "Run anyway"
6. Click the large "Activation" button and wait for the process to complete
7. You should see a confirmation message indicating successful activation
8. **Re-enable your antivirus software immediately**
9. Restart your computer to finalize the activation

---

## Features

• **Multiple Activation Modes** – KMS emulation, Auto Mode, status checking
• **Broad Compatibility** – Windows Vista to 11, Windows Server, Office 2010-2024+
• **Portable Application** – No installation required; runs from USB drive
• **Auto-Renewal Function** – Maintains activation beyond 180-day cycle
• **Multi-Language Interface** – English, Russian, and others
• **Custom KMS Server Support** – For advanced users

